company'),(1702,201,'_content_1_title','field_576434dff1a0e'),(1703,201,'content_1_secondary_title',''),(1704,201,'_content_1_secondary_title','field_576bbfccfea06'),(1705,201,'content_1_content','Since 1946, Heide &amp; Cook has been deeply rooted in the Hawaiian community. As a kama`aina company (literally meaning child of the land), we understand that in order to have a strong business, we also need to support a strong community.\r\n\r\nHeide and Cook proudly sponsors local community events through volunteerism, sponsorship and charitable giving in order to enrich the lives and those of our family, friends and neighbors.\r\n\r\nWherever you find a local youth sports program, charity golf outing, walk-a-thon, bike-a-thon, swim-a-thon, charity run or other community activity, you will find Heide &amp; Cook team members offering their support and participation. Our employees serve as mentors for our keiki (children), caregivers for our kupuna (ancestors and grandparents) and everyone in between.\r\n\r\nClick below to read more about our community involvement.'),(1706,201,'_content_1_content','field_576434e5f1a0f'),(1707,201,'content_1_button_text','Check out our blog'),(1708,201,'_content_1_button_text','field_576434f4f1a10'),(1709,201,'content_1_button_url','http://hcooke.wpengine.com/blog'),(1710,201,'_content_1_button_url','field_5764350ff1a11'),(1711,201,'content_1_image','482'),(1712,201,'_content_1_image','field_578830bf48514'),(1713,205,'_edit_lock','1481667630:7'),(1714,205,'_edit_last','7'),(1715,205,'header_style','standard'),(1716,205,'_header_style','field_576794782fa14'),(1717,205,'title','CAREERS AT HEIDE & COOK'),(1718,205,'_title','field_57857b4a8a802'),(1719,205,'secondary_title','Growing Together'),(1720,205,'_secondary_title','field_576798d8b0d92'),(1721,205,'header_image','316'),(1722,205,'_header_image','field_57679a0624866'),(1723,205,'content','a:3:{i:0;s:15:\"horizontal_menu\";i:1;s:19:\"content_two_columns\";i:2;s:12:\"content_grid\";}'),(17