0'),(4345,339,'content_0_button_url','htttps://google.com'),(4346,339,'_content_0_button_url','field_5764350ff1a11'),(4347,339,'content_0_image','342'),(4348,339,'_content_0_image','field_578830bf48514'),(4349,339,'content_1_title','Capabilities'),(4350,339,'_content_1_title','field_57643ef9183c7'),(4351,339,'content_1_blocks_0_image','520'),(4352,339,'_content_1_blocks_0_image','field_57643c80c43c1'),(4353,339,'content_1_blocks_0_title','Account Representative'),(4354,339,'_content_1_blocks_0_title','field_57643c96c43c2'),(4355,339,'content_1_blocks_0_content','For small facilities without complicated or mixed uses, customers may use their own office manager, buyer or senior operations person to manage facility services. In this scenario, Heide &amp; Cook can provided a single point of contact to help schedule services, address administrative issues and consult with the customer for special projects or non-routine issues.'),(4356,339,'_content_1_blocks_0_content','field_57643c9cc43c3'),(4357,339,'content_1_blocks_1_image','505'),(4358,339,'_content_1_blocks_1_image','field_57643c80c43c1'),(4359,339,'content_1_blocks_1_title','Facility Management Professional'),(4360,339,'_content_1_blocks_1_title','field_57643c96c43c2'),(4361,339,'content_1_blocks_1_content','When the need for knowledge or experience goes beyond the basics, customers can turn to Heide &amp; Cooks Facility Management Professionals (FMP). Certified by IFMA to the FMP level or by BOMI to a certificate level (e.g. FMC or SMC), our professionals have the expertise to address routine facility management issues, and can work with owners and vendors to develop asset lists and management plans, maintenance plans and strategies and reports  as well as assist with vendor management.'),(4362,339,'_content_1_blocks_1_content','field_57643c9cc43c3'),(4363,339,'content_1_blocks_2_image','345'),(4364,339,'_content_1_blocks_2_image','field_57643c80c43c1'),(4365,339,'content_1_blocks_2_title','Certified Facility Man