\n\r\n<strong>Community Involvement</strong>: We take pride in serving our community and its surrounding areas through support programs, physical and monetary donations.'),(6130,116,'_content_2_content','field_576bc36a18f4f'),(6131,116,'content_2_button_text','Contact Us'),(6132,116,'_content_2_button_text','field_576bc36a18f50'),(6133,116,'content_2_button_type','contact'),(6134,116,'_content_2_button_type','field_5788304f84c7f'),(6135,116,'content_2_image','427'),(6136,116,'_content_2_image','field_5762df199efe8'),(6137,116,'content_3_title','Our Partners'),(6138,116,'_content_3_title','field_57643a5865c12'),(6139,116,'content_3_secondary_title',''),(6140,116,'_content_3_secondary_title','field_576bbfccfea06'),(6141,116,'content_3_content','Our mission provides the framework for achieving our ambitious, long-term vision: Heide &amp; Cook will be the premier integrated facilities services provider across the islands.'),(6142,116,'_content_3_content','field_576bc36a18f4f'),(6143,116,'content_3_button_text','Contact Us'),(6144,116,'_content_3_button_text','field_576bc36a18f50'),(6145,116,'content_3_button_type','contact'),(6146,116,'_content_3_button_type','field_5788304f84c7f'),(6147,116,'content_3_image','442'),(6148,116,'_content_3_image','field_576bc36a18f52'),(6169,116,'_yoast_wpseo_title','Our Mission, Vision & Values | Heide & Cook'),(6170,116,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Heide & Cook is a mission-driven company aiming to set the standard of excellence for integrated facilities services providers across the islands. Learn more.'),(6205,60,'_edit_lock','1481947528:6'),(6206,19,'_edit_lock','1481952084:6'),(6207,116,'content_2_accordion_0_title','Excellence'),(6208,116,'_content_2_accordion_0_title','field_5762dd51d7d6f'),(6209,116,'content_2_accordion_0_content','We reflect <em>pono</em> (the Hawaiian term for excellence, goodness and moral qualities) in everything we do. We strive to do right by our customers, employees and community.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),(6210,116,'_c