nd deflector sheaves, correcting installation deficiencies from the previous elevator modernization project.'),(6487,457,'_details_3_content','field_57632a4cfc99d'),(6488,457,'details_4_title','Solution'),(6489,457,'_details_4_title','field_57632a1cfc99c'),(6490,457,'details_4_content','Heide &amp; Cook addressed small and large maintenance items to improve the overall performance and reliability of the elevator equipment at Camelot Condominium. The customer benefited with significantly reduced machine brake noise, improved performance times and enhanced car comfort and appearance. All of these items improved overall reliability and comfort and enhanced the property value. This project demonstrates our commitment to providing safe and reliable elevators for our customers.'),(6491,457,'_details_4_content','field_57632a4cfc99d'),(6492,457,'_dp_original','103'),(6493,458,'_wp_attached_file','2016/08/Camelot-Condominium-e1472511506357.png'),(6494,458,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:600;s:6:\"height\";i:558;s:4:\"file\";s:46:\"2016/08/Camelot-Condominium-e1472511506357.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:7:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:31:\"Camelot-Condominium-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:31:\"Camelot-Condominium-300x279.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:279;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:12:\"medium_large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:31:\"Camelot-Condominium-768x714.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:768;s:6:\"height\";i:714;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:6:\"slider\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:31:\"Camelot-Condominium-680x450.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:680;s:6:\"height\";i:450;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:6:\"header\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:32:\"Camelot-Condominium-1400x400.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:1400;s:6:\"height\";i:400;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:12:\"case_teasers\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:31:\"Camelot-Condominium-680x632.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:680;s:6:\