cfc99d'),(7008,101,'details_4_title','Solution'),(7009,101,'_details_4_title','field_57632a1cfc99c'),(7010,101,'details_4_content','<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: Calibri;\">Heide &amp; Cook designed and installed a new freezer/chiller walk-in combo with 14 retail glass doors, piped in new evaporative fan coil units, installed open display refrigerated cases and a number of under-the-counter units. All of the equipment was selected with energy-efficient motors and specially designed Mitsubishi Inverter Condensing Units. The project also included the installation ofLED lighting and energy-saving digital controls.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: Calibri;\">The entire project was designed to meet the demanding goals of 7-Eleven. Heide &amp; Cook delivered the new complex system on budget and ahead of schedule. The installation met all of the rigorous 7-Eleven standards prior to the construction deadline opening another energy efficient and convenient location.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),(7011,101,'_details_4_content','field_57632a4cfc99d'),(7012,101,'_yoast_wpseo_primary_case_studies_tags','14'),(7013,101,'_yoast_wpseo_content_score','30'),(7020,492,'header_style','video'),(7021,492,'_header_style','field_576794782fa14'),(7022,492,'title',''),(7023,492,'_title','field_57857b4a8a802'),(7024,492,'secondary_title','Your One-Stop-Shop for Building Maintenance in Hawaii'),(7025,492,'_secondary_title','field_576798d8b0d92'),(7026,492,'header_image','215'),(7027,492,'_header_image','field_57679a0624866'),(7028,492,'video_title','About Us'),(7029,492,'_video_title','field_57721330067bb'),(7030,492,'video','http://players.brightcove.net/921263834001/default_default/index.html?videoId=5103718780001'),(7031,492,'_video','field_576794ad2fa15'),(7032,492,'submenu','none'),(7033,492,'_submenu','field_5788332f82648'),(7034,492,'content_0_title','All Your Facility Needs, All Under One Roof'),(7035,492,'_content_0_title','field_5762cef6de35a'),(7036,492